{"tid":376350,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓綜] 推理愛情節目: Heart Signal","createTime":"2017-08-27T02:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T10:25:02.000Z","uid":36496,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3496eddbf17bff95ca1d3bc265aede693931c9","tid":376350,"uid":36496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"《Heart Signal》（韓語：하트시그널，英語：Heart Signal）是韓國Channel A於2017年製作的綜藝節目，由尹鍾信、李尚敏、神童、金伊娜、沈素英、楊宰雄等人主持，主軸以製作組尋找6位年輕男女於「信號小屋」（位於首爾鐘路區上岩洞）中合宿一個月，並於其中彼此之間出現的信號進行推理愛情節目。<br />\n若主持人猜測正確，可獲得愛的原石（鑽石）一顆，一顆原石相當於韓圓50萬元（新台幣1萬3千四百多元；美金四百四十多元；日幣4萬8千一百多元），但主持人們唯有累積至最後一期，並答對最後一期的題目後，方可將原石換成現金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5JuBK6_7s6o/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F5JuBK6_7s6o%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f2d718c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中字: <a href=\"http://www.helloidol.com/26009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.helloidol.com%2F26009.html&d=qwbY4yp6nOJo4LhtWdkQJW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e42d1169\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.helloidol.com/26009.html</a><br />\n<br />\n總共12集, 岩岩完左, 中字就譯到第5集. 有無巴絲有睇, 真係好正, 上曬癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f7da202cbd99950d76c0758a53653f96de4d39","tid":376350,"uid":85993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一追就睇晒五集<br />\n個人唔太鐘意張天<br />\n但個個女人都鐘意佢"},{"pid":"e30edd8fb81c09ca69c0ab782830cb3a229f8b90","tid":376350,"uid":36496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"女參加者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.chosun.com/sitedata/image/201706/15/2017061502058_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.chosun.com%2Fsitedata%2Fimage%2F201706%2F15%2F2017061502058_1.jp